Uses of Class
FESI.Exceptions.EcmaScriptException

Packages that use EcmaScriptException
FESI.Data Contains all native FESI objects. 
FESI.Exceptions Contains the exceptions specific to FESI, but without JSException which is defined in jslib. 
FESI.Extensions Contains the standard Extensions. 
FESI.Interpreter Contains the interpreter itself (the xxxVisitor classes), then driver routines (Evaluator), the interactive interpreter (Interpret) and may utility classes.
